{
  "stem": "4247.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was, as, as I said to you, the time when there must have been a lot of soul-searching happening amongst the Hungarian leaders, which eventually culminated on the 15th of October by the so-called Horthy proclamation.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know who Horthy was--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the regent, the number one man in Hungary, who, by that time, realized that the war is well and truly lost.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he read a proclamation into a-- into the radio declaring, declaring Hungary's, Hungary's neutrality, right, in the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember very crystal clear-- and it was on a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was at my uncle's-- my baker uncle's-- house-- flat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He lived quite luxuriously [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] measured by the times.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we heard this proclamation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everybody was joyful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, well, that's the end of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I walked to-- he lived on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I walked to the window.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I saw the German soldiers on the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said to him-- his name was Ernie, Ernie, Ernie [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Ernie [NON-ENGLISH], that's not the end yet, the worst is yet to come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was very angry with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said that I'm-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what is the best word in Hungarian to translate it?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[HUNGARIAN]-- I'm, I'm, I'm the-- I'm the-- I'm the carrier of, of bad news.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How would you say that in English?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would say a doomsayer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A doomsayer, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the right, right translation from [HUNGARIAN], which is in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to him, well, I hope that I'm wrong, Ernie [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But unfortunately, I was right.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans didn't take it lying down, as it was expected.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
